{"tid":1292282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東省擬建大灣區信用評分制度　 香港澳門都要參與 　三地互通資料","createTime":"2019-07-07T08:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T09:31:21.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"78883a016fd692177868d581961a9812edaebd0d","tid":1292282,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"中國正建立信用評分制度，為人員進行信用評分，目標以對欠缺信用人士作出更大制裁。而這個制度或許在數年內會對港人產生影響。據報廣東省將策劃粵港澳信用評分制度，對企業實行信用獎勵與懲罰措施。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n根據香港《有線新聞》報道，廣東省正式提出了粵港澳大灣區在未來 3 年，會推出信用評分制度。此制度把香港、澳門亦包括在內。廣東省希望藉此計劃，能夠讓大灣區共享信用信息，依法對大灣區內企業，實施信用激勵和失信懲戒。計劃亦提到，需要推動中國大陸與港澳的信息互通、加強警務合作交流，應對傳統與非傳統的安全威脅。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n中國大陸的社會信用評分制度其中一個開發商，是阿里巴巴旗下螞蟻金服運營的「芝麻信用」，該平台數據來自社交網絡、公共與私人機構平台，挖掘個人留下的數據軌跡，從而獲得完整的社交檔案，包括：位置信息、好友、健康記錄、保險、私人消息、財務狀況、遊戲時間、智能家居統計、首選報紙、購物記錄以及約會行為。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n不過《有線新聞》亦引述學者指出，由於三地政制有別，港人資料被牽涉在內的機會不大，估計被共享的資料只會是中國大陸方面的黑名單資料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ww.facebook.com/watch/?v=452677845522585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D452677845522585&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=cc8d5f85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ww.facebook.com/watch/?v=452677845522585</a>"},{"pid":"ae34761aec2e472c2888aa6160f9e864ce01c359","tid":1292282,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港人資料被牽涉在內的機會不大</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7ad29cc0ff6a3e7eaeefe177e5565a7d1b6ba1","tid":1292282,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ae34761aec2e472c2888aa6160f9e864ce01c359","tid":1292282,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港人資料被牽涉在內的機會不大</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:50:20.000Z","msg":"因為有私隱條例 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c8a505a6e5f7896c4f2b14cc3d8514d7145e5b","tid":1292282,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"無用<br />\n你點都唔肯自由開放<br />\n學人搞大灣區徙有虛名"},{"pid":"a7ed89adc174d5c5e7e784247c958db71c5ea053","tid":1292282,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f7ad29cc0ff6a3e7eaeefe177e5565a7d1b6ba1","tid":1292282,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ae34761aec2e472c2888aa6160f9e864ce01c359","tid":1292282,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港人資料被牽涉在內的機會不大</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:50:20.000Z","msg":"因為有私隱條例 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}